title: Biggenden Meatworks accident leaves worker fighting for life | Perth Now
text:
Biggenden Meatworks accident leaves worker fighting for life AAP February 21, 2017 1:56pm 
A MAN is fighting for life after a workplace accident south of Bundaberg. 
Paramedics said the man, aged in his late 30s or early 40s, suffered significant head and facial injuries about 8.30am today and was airlifted to Bundaberg Hospital following treatment at Biggenden Hospital. 
The incident is believed to have happened at Biggenden Meatworks.
